287
00:21:52,573 --> 00:21:54,438
Do you want to get better or not?

288
00:21:54,474 --> 00:21:55,266
I do. I just...

289
00:21:55,291 --> 00:21:57,642
Then throw out the Paco
Rabanne and the chopsticks.

290
00:21:57,678 --> 00:21:59,610
Start taking your antihistamines.

291
