00:25:47,934 --> 00:25:50,201
She liked me.

347
00:25:51,670 --> 00:25:54,038
We drank.

348
00:25:55,408 --> 00:25:58,009
We went to bed.

349
00:25:58,044 --> 00:26:02,813
Woke up in the kitchen. I
