00:26:14,126 --> 00:26:16,259
Even if you can't remember
anything, you'd know that.

353
00:26:16,295 --> 00:26:20,397
You'd feel it, right? I don't.

354
00:26:20,432 --> 00:26:24,467
- I'm not a murderer.
- Of course you're not.

355
00:26:24,502 --> 00:26:26,536
I'm so sorry I did this to you.

356
00:26:26,571 --> 00:26:30,506
Listen, you
didn't do anything, huh?

357
00:26:30,542 --> 00:26:34,110
The jury, they'll see
right past, uh, the...

358
00:26:34,146 --> 00:26:39,849
the so-called evidence and the lawyers
and all this, and they'll see you.

359
00:26:49,461 --> 00:26:52,962
At, uh, 2:30 a.m. Saturday morning,

360
00:26:52,997 --> 00:26:55,497
a 22-year-old woman, Andrea Cornish,

361
00:26:55,532 --> 00:26:59,634
was found stabbed to death in
her home on West 87th Street.

362
00:26:59,670 --> 00:27:02,438
Less than a quarter-mile
away from the murder scene,

363
00:27:02,473 --> 00:27:05,841
a 23-year-old male, Nasir Khan,

364
00:27:05,876 --> 00:27:09,177
was detained by officers
on suspicion of DUI.

365
00:27:09,212 --> 00:27:13,715
While in custody, a knife believed to be
