368
00:27:24,594 --> 00:27:26,260
<i>What
was their relationship?</i>

369
00:27:26,296 --> 00:27:28,262
<i>That's under investigation.</i>

370
00:27:28,298 --> 00:27:30,398
<i>Do you have
a motive for the killing?</i>

371
00:27:30,433 --> 00:27:32,233
<i>At this point, it looks
sexual in nature,</i>

372
00:27:32,268 --> 00:27:35,069
<i>but that, too, is under investigation.</i>

373
00:27:35,105 --> 00:27:37,771
<i>Is the suspect a citizen?</i>

374
00:27:37,807 --> 00:27:39,673
<i>The records show
he was born here, yes.</i>

375
00:27:39,709 --> 00:27:40,492
Thank you.

376
00:27:40,517 --> 00:27:42,842
<i>But he's Muslim.
Is that right?</i>

377
00:27:42,877 --> 00:27:46,413
<i>- We understand he is.</i>
<i>- Does he have ties</i>

378
00:27:46,448 --> 00:27:48,214
<i>to any foreign organizations?</i>

379
00:27:48,250 --> 00:27:50,150
<i>That's under investigation.</i>

380
00:27:50,185 --> 00:27:54,154
Organizations. What organizations?
What are they saying?

381
00:27:54,189 --> 00:27:56,556
You know what they are saying.

382
00:27:56,591 --> 00:27:59,025
<i>Does he have a
history of violent crimes?</i>

383
00:27:59,060 --> 00:28:01,326
<i>That, too,
is under investigation.</i>

384
00:28:01,362 --> 00:28:03,863
<i>That's all I have for you right now.
I'll update you</i>

385
00:28:03,898 --> 00:28:05,865
when we have more information.
Thank you.

386
00:28:12,840 --> 00:28:15,007
Hey, come here.

387
00:28:15,043 --> 00:28:18,977
Got something to say, okay?
You ready? You rolling?

388
00:28:19,012 --> 00:28:23,014
"Foreign organizations."
