389
00:28:23,050 --> 00:28:24,649
My client was born here.

390
00:28:24,685 --> 00:28:27,719
<i>He's as American as baseball.</i>
Detective Williams, please.

391
00:28:27,754 --> 00:28:31,256
<i>What are they gonna do next, look
