00:29:08,594 --> 00:29:09,860
No.

396
00:29:25,210 --> 00:29:28,978
- From Freddy.
- Who?

397
00:29:33,418 --> 00:29:34,817
What for?

398
00:29:37,389 --> 00:29:39,355
Traction.

399
00:30:55,832 --> 00:30:56,864
Yeah. It's here.

400
00:30:56,899 --> 00:30:58,298
Great. What do we pay?

401
00:30:58,334 --> 00:30:59,700
Nothing till it's released.

402
00:30:59,736 --> 00:31:01,602
That's why we're here.

403
00:31:01,637 --> 00:31:02,936
You can't have it now.

404
00:31:02,971 --> 00:31:04,638
If you'd have called, I
could have told you that.

405
00:31:04,673 --> 00:31:06,440
Well, we have to come
back to get it. When?

406
00:31:06,475 --> 00:31:08,808
After the trial, or never.

407
00:31:08,844 --> 00:31:12,078
- Excuse me?
- It's your cab?

408
00:31:12,114 --> 00:31:16,049
It's ours, the three of us all together.

409
00:31:16,084 --> 00:31:18,284
Then you should all get lawyers.

410
00:31:18,319 --> 00:31:19,685
What are you talking about?

411
00:31:19,721 --> 00:31:21,855
The cab was used in the
commission of a crime,

412
00:31:21,890 --> 00:31:25,225
which means the state can sue in
order to keep it in a civil court.

413
00:31:25,260 --> 00:31:27,093
Sue? Sue who?

414
00:31:27,129 --> 00:31:28,862
You, the registered owners.

415
00:31:28,897 --> 00:31:30,830
But the suit won't get filed
until the criminal trial

416
00:31:30,866 --> 00:31:32,665
and however many months that'll take,

417
00:31:32,700 --> 00:31:35,301
which I could have told you over the
phone if you'd have called first.

418
00:31:35,336 --> 00:31:36,835
- Months?
- Or longer.

419
00:31:36,871 --> 00:31:39,405
Slow wheels of justice and all.
And I hate to say it,

420
00:31:39,440 --> 00:31:42,508
but you'll probably lose in civil court.

421
00:31:42,543 --> 00:31:46,979
Unless, uh... which of you is Khan?

422
00:31:47,014 --> 00:31:49,749
Him.

423
00:31:51,685 --> 00:31:54,719
- Is it your relative, sir?
- What?

424
00:31:54,755 --> 00:31:57,355
- Is it your relative who's been charged?
