425
00:31:57,391 --> 00:31:59,557
Did he have permission
from you to drive the cab?

426
00:31:59,593 --> 00:32:01,326
Not really.

427
00:32:01,361 --> 00:32:02,795
Well, then that's your out.

428
00:32:02,830 --> 00:32:04,629
