431
00:32:09,736 --> 00:32:13,037
Hey, I'm just trying
to help you guys out.

432
00:32:17,177 --> 00:32:19,010
I'm no lawyer, but if he won't do it,

433
00:32:19,045 --> 00:32:22,180
