439
00:33:42,293 --> 00:33:46,961
Here you go. I come bearing gifts.

440
00:34:39,581 --> 00:34:41,748
Don't worry. I
won't put you on YouTube.

441
00:34:41,783 --> 00:34:45,652
Don't even joke around like that.
Come on.

442
00:34:48,223 --> 00:34:52,425
- Can I open it?
- I didn't say you could.

443
00:35:17,551 --> 00:35:18,750
Check the fridge.

444
00:35:18,786 --> 00:35:21,120
You check the fridge.

445
00:35:35,402 --> 00:35:37,135
Here you go.

446
00:36:47,372 --> 00:36:50,106
Chandra. That's right, isn't it?

447
00:36:50,141 --> 00:36:53,042
- Yes.
- Come here.

448
00:36:56,013 --> 00:36:58,013
- Crowe and Associates.
- Where you from?

449
00:36:58,049 --> 00:37:00,849
- Um, Baltimore.
